[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0496","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0496.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0771","title":"Compaq Survey Utility Web 文件访问 - 目录遍历（CVE-1999-0771）","description":"Compaq Management Agents 和 Compaq Survey Utility 的网络组件允许远程攻击者通过使用「..」攻击（目录遍历）来读取任意文件。此漏洞影响多个版本，包括 Compaq Client Management Agents 4.0+，Survey Utility 2.0+，以及相关的 Insight Manager、Intelligent Cluster Administrator Management Agents 等产品。攻击者无需身份验证即可访问 Web 管理组件，并通过 URL 中包含目录遍历序列「../」的请求来读取目标系统上的敏感文件，例如 WinNT/repair/sam._ 文件或 NetWare 系统上的 ldremote.ncf 文件。漏洞原理在于 Web 服务器未能验证所请求的路径是否超出了其文档树范围。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0771"],"sources":["nvd"],"published":"1999-05-26","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到 HP Management Agents 的最新支持版本或确保已应用最新的补丁；如果产品已停止支持，建议彻底卸载 Survey Utility 和 Web 管理组件，并改用受支持的 HP 管理方案替代；禁用 Web 管理组件的远程访问功能；在防火墙级别限制仅允许受信任管理 IP 访问 Web 管理端口 (通常为 2301)。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0771","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19225","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0771"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0496.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1102","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1102.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1414","title":"IBM Netfinity Remote Control 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"IBM Netfinity Remote Control 软件的进程管理器以系统级权限运行，本地攻击者可通过该进程管理器启动任意程序，从而获得管理员权限并执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 IBM Remote Control Software 1.0 版本，CVSS 评分为 7.2，危害等级为高危。攻击者需要具备目标系统的本地访问权限才能利用此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1414"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-05-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:23.410","remediation":"立即升级到 IBM Netfinity Manager 的修复版本，或安装 IBM 官方提供的安全补丁。如无法立即升级，可执行以下缓解措施：限制 WNETFIN 目录的文件级权限，禁止普通用户执行 Netfinity Manager Services；通过 Netfinity Security Manager 禁用 Process Manager 和 Remote Session 组件；将服务账户从 SYSTEM/ADMINISTRATOR 降级为普通用户账户以限制权限；修改 INSTALL.INI 配置文件，阻止 Process Manager 和 Remote Session 的安装。最终建议卸载 IBM Netfinity Remote Control Software 并替换为更安全的远程管理方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92765856706547&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92902484317769&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/284","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19227","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e2d7ee098b36909e6f1960d9a77b8043812c482f/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1414.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1414","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1414.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2301e36f8af0694b1f220afdc97e9e07ee9e6a52/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1414.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hvvc-66wm-g462/GHSA-hvvc-66wm-g462.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1414.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--341a5abc-54a6-489c-9418-616b61d4fb96.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1102.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0539","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0539.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0803","title":"IBM AIX eNetwork Firewall 不安全临时文件创建漏洞","description":"IBM AIX eNetwork Firewall 3.2 与 3.3 版本中的 fwluser 脚本在创建临时文件时未采取安全的文件创建方式，存在不安全临时文件创建漏洞。本地已登录的普通用户可利用符号链接（symlink）攻击手段，在脚本写入临时文件的过程中将链接指向任意系统文件，从而以脚本运行权限覆盖或写入目标文件内容。该漏洞影响运行上述版本防火墙软件的 AIX 系统，攻击条件为攻击者需具备本地账户并能在脚本执行期间实施符号链接替换，利用方式相对简单，CVSS 基础评分 2.1，危害等级较低，但可能导致本地文件被篡改或权限提升。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0803"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-05-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.407","remediation":"建议升级至 IBM AIX eNetwork Firewall 3.4 或更高版本（已修复该临时文件竞争条件）。若无法升级，请为 /tmp 目录启用粘滞位（chmod +t /tmp），并限制 fwluser 脚本的写入权限（chmod 755 /usr/lpp/fw/bin/fwluser），同时在防火墙层面禁止非受信本地用户登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92765973207648&w=2","http://www.osvdb.org/962","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19229","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/770e8f09ce14e637a09c7c619e10772aa6172bea/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0803.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0803","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0803.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e1298ff7aafe81b936ca67ecef34c3124d6c72f0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0803.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2a2be81fd4b47dc35d815a995b6429bd116a3b84/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-59f5-phf9-mq45/GHSA-59f5-phf9-mq45.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0803.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--53295666-d1a4-44a0-9681-9213e3b76b09.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0539.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0539.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0539.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0478","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0478.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0762","title":"Netscape Communicator about 协议信息泄露漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 浏览器在处理 HTML 页面时存在信息泄露漏洞。当页面的 TITLE 标签中嵌入 JavaScript 代码时，远程攻击者可利用浏览器的 \"about:\" 协议访问浏览器内部敏感信息（如历史记录、书签或配置数据）。该漏洞影响 Netscape Communicator 的多个早期版本，攻击条件为用户访问攻击者控制的恶意网页。攻击者通过构造包含特定 JavaScript 的 HTML 页面，诱导用户点击访问，即可在无需身份认证的情况下窃取浏览器信息，造成隐私泄露。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0762"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:00.337","remediation":"升级 Netscape Communicator 至 4.51 或更高版本（该版本已修复通过“about”协议读取浏览器信息的问题）。若无法立即升级，可在浏览器配置中禁用 JavaScript 执行（编辑 prefs.js 设置 javascript.enabled=false）或通过网络代理/防火墙规则拦截含有 about: 协议的异常请求，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0762","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e268305fd8644994d337819e469d1f89bafde833/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0762.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0762","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0762.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0ea6b1a1298433599abdd2a4c6b6ce9f09476665/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0762.json","https://