S 9 或更高版本可从根本上消除此漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1393.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1393","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1393.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1393.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gh96-8q4m-h947/GHSA-gh96-8q4m-h947.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/532/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1393.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000643.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1096.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0312","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0312.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0715","title":"Microsoft Windows NT RAS Phonebook 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 系列系统的远程访问服务（RAS）客户端在解析电话簿条目时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可通过构造恶意的电话簿文件并诱使用户在 RAS 连接中打开该条目，触发溢出后可在目标系统上执行任意命令或造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及 SP1 至 SP5 所有版本，攻击条件要求能够诱导用户导入或打开特制电话簿文件。Microsoft 已发布 MS99-030 安全公告对此漏洞进行修复，建议受影响用户下载并安装官方补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0715"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-20T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:54.323","remediation":"建议立即安装 Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 的 RAS Phonebook 漏洞安全补丁（Microsoft Security Bulletin MS99-020，对应补丁 Q194693）。如无法立即打补丁，可暂时停用 Remote Access Service (RAS) 服务，并限制普通用户对相关 .pbk 电话簿文件及 RAS 配置目录的写权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ230677","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-016","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19211","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64d76d92cfbd9c4de4a352a59a2e52cadebc3afd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0715.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0715","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0715.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/89b3a1c34ab26afed5cfe4fc54b61cecbf09d3c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0715.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1dbd44058e428445290bfb1f6fc6ecc0addbfd35/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w83x-7v2j-2q4m/GHSA-w83x-7v2j-2q4m.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/1999/CVE-1999-0715.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/akabe1/windows_exploit_dowser/blob/11b24e36173cd382721db28581e575faf687d06b/cve_from_exploitdb_website.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0312.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0886","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0886.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1031","title":"Behold Software Web Page Counter counter.exe 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Behold Software Web Page Counter 2.70 版本中的 counter.exe 程序存在拒绝服务漏洞。该程序在处理外部请求时未对传入参数长度进行合法性校验，远程攻击者无需身份认证，只需向运行该计数器的服务发送一个包含超长参数的请求（如通过 URL 传递过长的 argument），即可触发程序异常挂起（hang），导致服务无法正常响应后续请求，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响所有运行 Behold Software Web Page Counter 2.70 且暴露 counter.exe 的 Web 服务器，攻击门槛低、可远程利用，虽不造成代码执行，但会中断网站正常的访问统计与页面服务。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1031"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:33.700","remediation":"建议立即停用 Behold Software Web Page Counter 2.70 的 counter.exe 组件，或升级至厂商发布的最新版本（如有）。若业务必须保留，可在 Web 服务器层面配置请求长度限制（如 IIS 的 maxUrlLength/maxQueryString），并在防火墙层面拦截异常长参数请求作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92713790426690&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92707671717292&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/267","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/067b58f5ad5d89a104fab4ddd25fa3685c59a18e/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1031.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1031","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1031.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6fc85c731fb3018b2c4fbe9aed66186edd5321b/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1031.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hmhc-wx7p-hg6x/GHSA-hmhc-wx7p-hg6x.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/267/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1031.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--28c20fd4-a809-4902-a161-17fb0ded9ae4.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0886.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0886.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0886.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0885","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0885.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1030","title":"Behold Software Web Page Counter 2.70 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Behold Software Web Page Counter 2.70 版本的 counter.exe 存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过发送以 %0A（换行符）结尾的恶意 HTTP 请求，导致计数器日志记录畸形条目并触发访问冲突，使计数器程序挂起从而造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Behold Software Web Page Counter 2.70 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，属于中危级别拒绝服务漏洞，攻击者无需认证即可远程发起攻击，只需发送特制 HTTP 请求即可触发漏洞导致服务不可用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1030"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:33.570","remediation":"升级 Behold Software Web Page Counter 至修复该问题的后续版本（避免使用 2.70 的 counter.exe）。如无法立即升级，可在 Web 服务器（如 IIS）中配置 URL 重写或请求过滤规则，拦截包含 %0A（换行符）的 HTTP 请求，并在前端防火墙/反向代理处丢弃此类畸形请求，防止恶意换行写入计数器日志导致 counter.exe 访问违规而挂起。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92713790426690&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92707671717292&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/267","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19212","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7e65fa522cff0172990568230ff9b719b8650296/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1030.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1030","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1030.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6fc85c731fb3018b2c4fbe9aed66186edd5321b/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1030.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/counter.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1030.json","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5707ac17-5923-4f38-badf-6ea549fb932d.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0885.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0885.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0885.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0686","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0686.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0765","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9143,\"outputTokens\":19,\"totalTokens\":10826}}","description":"SGI IRIX 6.5.4 中的 midikeys 程序存在本地权限提升漏洞，该程序以 root 权限运行且允许本地用户通过文本编辑器修改任意文件。本地攻击者可利用该缺陷修改系统关键配置文件（如 /etc/passwd 或 sudoers 文件），从而提升权限至 root。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.5.4 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0（严重），攻击条件为本地用户账户访问权限，利用方式为通过 midikeys 程序调用文本编辑器修改关键系统文件实现提权。SGI 已发布补丁修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0765"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:00.710","remediation":"建议立即移除 midikeys 程序的 setuid root 权限：`chmod u-s /usr/sbin/midikeys`，或升级到 SGI IRIX 6.5.5 及以上版本。如无法升级，可通过删除 midikeys 可执行权限 `chmod 000 /usr/sbin/midikeys` 作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/262","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19210","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e244b55bdff85b2483c0e6a7cecd12f8bee0df6e/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0765.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0765","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0765.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0ea6b1a1298433599abdd2a4c6b6ce9f09476665/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0765.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d9ad03f9df46533ce9229f9da6bbf66bd77a3f4f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-4wg8-h27h-453j/GHSA-4wg8-h27h-453j.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0765.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--c5545578-048e-4acc-97a2-487c23d98355.json","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--c5545578-048e-4acc-97a2-487c23d98355.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0686.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0686.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0686.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0985","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0985.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1156","title":"BisonWare FTP Server PORT命令拒绝服务漏洞","description":"BisonWare FTP Server 4.1 及更早版本存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标 FTP 服务的 PORT 命令发送包含非数字字符及大量回车符的畸形数据包，导致 FTP 服务进程崩溃或停止响应，造成拒绝服务。攻击无需身份认证，仅需网络可达即可触发，利用难度较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1156"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:50.407","remediation":"BisonWare FTP Server 已停止维护且厂商已倒闭，建议迁移至活跃维护的 FTP 服务器软件如 vsftpd 或 ProFTPD。迁移前作为临时缓解措施，可在网络边界防火墙或 IPS 设备上添加规则，过滤包含大量回车符的畸形 FTP PORT 命令，并限制允许连接 FTP 服务的源 IP 范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2254","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1156.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1156","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1156.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1156.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-phmx-3wr6-q2h6/GHSA-phmx-3wr6-q2h6.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_500_600.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-241.txt","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/35c40c2c96029682f9c3da862749763b6c97e1fb/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-11xx/CVE-1999-1156.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000639.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/be7ad03fdf3a412f0fd57a25f1732dc0ecfb1cb3/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0985.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0315","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0315.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0716","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9224,\"outputTokens\":20,\"totalTokens\":10908}}","description":"Windows NT 4.0 帮助文件实用程序（help file utility）在处理格式错误的帮助文件（.hlp/.chm）时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过诱骗用户打开特制的恶意帮助文件触发该漏洞，导致在目标系统上执行任意代码或造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 全系列版本（含 SP1 至 SP5），CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中等。攻击者通常将恶意帮助文件捆绑于邮件附件或下载链接中，诱导用户手动打开即可触发利用。Microsoft 已在后续安全更新中修复该漏洞，受影响用户应安装相应补丁并避免打开来源不明的帮助文件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0716"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:54.460","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 于 1999 年 5 月 17 日发布的安全公告 MS99-015 所附补丁（KB231605），或通过 Windows Update 自动更新以消除该漏洞。如补丁不适用于当前环境，应将系统升级至受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows Server 2012 R2 或更高版本）。作为临时缓解措施，将 %windir%\\Help 目录的写入权限限制为仅管理员，并禁止打开来源不明的 .hlp 帮助文件，同时部署应用控制策略阻止非授权帮助文件的执行。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ231605","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-015","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19209","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/1999/CVE-1999-0716.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/64d76d92cfbd9c4de4a352a59a2e52cadebc3afd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0716.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/89b3a1c34ab26afed5cfe4fc54b61cecbf09d3c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0716.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0716","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/bc3b224aa865bb4a5c31d7720dca83e446e475e2/1999/CVE-1999-0716.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/178b809924783e13787d17bb1b1fd55ad3b8639b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0716.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0716.md","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/ec2efce98d544aa857266906f720ae32e42b21be/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-07xx/CVE-1999-0716.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/f4098a65ae9e8440f9d959bbd974af1ed2176bec/1999/CVE-1999-0716.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0716.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0315.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0315.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0315.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1981","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1981.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1510","title":"BisonWare BisonFTP Server 3.5 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"BisonWare BisonFTP Server 3.5 及更早版本在处理 USER、LIST、CWD 等 FTP 命令时，对输入长度缺乏边界校验，存在多个栈缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程未授权攻击者可通过向 FTP 服务发送超长的命令参数触发溢出，导致服务崩溃造成拒绝服务，或在服务器进程权限下执行任意代码。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，攻击条件仅为网络可达目标 FTP 21 端口，影响范围覆盖 3.5 及之前版本，CVSS 评分为 7.5（高危）。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1510"],"sources":["exploitdb","cve"],"published":"1999-05-17","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"升级 BisonWare BisonFTP Server 至 4.1 或更高版本以修复命令解析中的缓冲区溢出。若无法立即升级，应在防火墙限制对 TCP 21 端口的访问，仅允许可信 IP 连接，并关闭匿名账户作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/17810","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3234","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92697301706956&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f56f639de76f94fc0aef783754a3de16fea7357b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1510.json","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1510"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/17810"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1981.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0208","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0208.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0489","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.0 未信任脚本粘贴漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 5.0 的 MSHTML.DLL 组件存在不可信脚本粘贴漏洞，远程攻击者可通过构造恶意网页，利用脚本将用户本地文件路径粘贴至文件上传内建控件中，从而在用户无感知的情况下强制上传任意本地文件。该漏洞属于 MS98-013 公告所述\"不可信脚本粘贴\"问题的变种，攻击者无需任何用户交互即可窃取敏感文件。影响 Internet Explorer 5.0 及可能更早版本，CVSS v2.0 评分为 10.0，危害严重。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0489"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-05-17","updated":"1999-05-17","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS98-013 提供的补丁，将 mshtml.dll 升级至 4.72.3509.0100 及以上版本。对于 Windows 98 用户，通过 Windows Update 获取关键更新。对于已停止支持的旧系统，建议升级至受支持的 Windows 版本并使用现代浏览器，同时在 IE 中禁用活动脚本和跨域访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0208.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0208.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1082","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1082.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1366","title":"Pegasus 邮件客户端 POP3 密码弱加密存储漏洞","description":"Pegasus 电子邮件客户端 3.0 及更早版本存在密码存储加密强度不足漏洞。程序将 POP3 账户密码使用弱加密算法处理后明文或近似明文存储在 pmail.ini 配置文件中，本地攻击者只需访问该文件即可轻易解密获取密码，进而读取目标用户的电子邮件内容。该漏洞利用门槛低，无需特殊权限，属于本地信息泄露风险。","severity":"LOW","score":3.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1366"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:17.223","remediation":"建议升级至 Pegasus Mail 3.1 及以上版本，该版本改进了 POP3 密码的加密存储方式。若无法升级，应限制对 pmail.ini 文件的本地访问权限，仅允许必要用户读取，并避免在多用户共享系统上使用该客户端处理敏感邮件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92714118829880&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/4e6f80460dd56d97b6079eb72c9467b9a961ce1b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1366.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1366","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1366.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1366.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h93v-m49q-355g/GHSA-h93v-m49q-355g.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1366.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000637.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/b929f4524cd5f55e84af4c34d9f33ee2512d5d4a/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--80679e4a-cea9-490e-88af-d157a83a5ea8.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1082.toml"}]